==How to be a furry and not get [[banned]]==
Leam can be found [[User:Leam|on ED]], and actually has lasted more than 3 minutes, unlike most furries.  To learn from his example and stay alive, you could try:
* Not [[vandal]]izing articles
* Not bitching about [[fursecution|FURSECUTION!!!]] on [[Encyclopedia Dramatica|ED]]
* Not [[Jeffree Star|flaunting your perversions]]
* Writing [[Encyclopedia_Dramatica:Today%27s_featured_article/September_3%2C_2006|featured articles]]
* Not being [[unfunny]] like most contributors to this article
